      "content": "that's a good start. but i want to make sure i preempt any counterarguments in my paper. like, people always bring up meritocracy or the idea that people should just keep what they earn. how should i frame those arguments so they don't undermine my point? i want to show why those views are basically outdated or logically flawed in the context of systemic racism.",
